    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just not that simple. i've tried all that. i've tried focusing on myself, i've tried finding \"my people,\" but it never works. it just feels like the more i try, the more i realize there's no point. why do i have to keep fighting this battle every single day if the outcome is always going to be the same? it feels like there's no real relief in life, just different versions of the same exhaustion.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
